        <h1><strong>🔐 Privacy Policy</strong></h1>
        <p>Effective as of March 11, 2025</p>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>FitHub Sdn Bhd</strong>! Your privacy is important to us. This <strong>Privacy Policy</strong> explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our services.</p>
        <p>By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in this <strong>Privacy Policy</strong>.</p>

        <h2><strong>1. 📥 Information We Collect</strong></h2>
        <p>We collect different types of personal data to provide better services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>📌 Personal Information:</strong> Contact details including name, email, telephone number and shipping, billing address. Login and account information, including screen name, password and unique user ID. Personal details including gender, hometown, date of birth and purchase history. Payment information (credit card details, e-wallets, cash payment records, etc). Images, photos and videos.</li>
            <li><strong>📌 Technical & Usage Data:</strong> IP address and device information. Browsing history, preferences, and interactions on our website. Cookies and tracking technologies.</li>
            <li><strong>📌 Transaction Data:</strong> Order history and purchased items. Payment details (including cash transactions) and receipts.</li>
            <li><strong>📌 Optional Information:</strong> If you sign up for newsletters or promotions, we may collect preferences and interests.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2><strong>2. 🛠️ How We Use Your Data</strong></h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>✅ Order Processing & Delivery:</strong> To confirm purchases, process payments, and ship products.</li>
            <li><strong>✅ Customer Support:</strong> To respond to inquiries, returns, and refunds.</li>
            <li><strong>✅ Marketing & Promotions:</strong> To send special offers, newsletters, and personalized recommendations (you can opt out anytime).</li>
            <li><strong>✅ Security & Fraud Prevention:</strong> To detect fraudulent activities and unauthorized transactions.</li>
            <li><strong>✅ Improving Our Services:</strong> To analyze website usage, fix bugs, and enhance user experience.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>We <strong>do not sell your data</strong> to third parties.</p>

        <h2><strong>3. 🍪 Cookies & Tracking Technologies</strong></h2>
        <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve your browsing experience. These include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>🍪 Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for website functionality (e.g., logging in, shopping cart).</li>
            <li><strong>🎯 Marketing & Advertising Cookies:</strong> Help us show relevant ads based on your interests.</li>
            <li><strong>📊 Analytics Cookies:</strong> Track website traffic and user behavior for improvements.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>

        <h2><strong>4. 🔄 Data Sharing & Third Parties</strong></h2>
        <p>We may share your data with trusted third parties only when necessary:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Payment Providers:</strong> To process transactions securely (e.g., Visa, Mastercard).</li>
            <li><strong>Logistics & Shipping Partners:</strong> To deliver your orders.</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> If required by law or for fraud prevention.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We <strong>never</strong> share your data with advertisers or third-party marketers without your consent.</p>

        <h2><strong>5. 🔒 How We Protect Your Data</strong></h2>
        <p>🔒 We take security seriously and use the following measures to protect your information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>✔️ Data Encryption:</strong> Your payment details and sensitive information are encrypted.</li>
            <li><strong>✔️ Secure Servers:</strong> We store data in secure environments with strict access controls.</li>
            <li><strong>✔️ Regular Security Audits:</strong> We monitor and update our security systems regularly.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>However, while we take precautions, no system is 100% secure. Always protect your personal information online.</em></p>

        <h2><strong>6. ⚖ ️Your Rights & Choices</strong></h2>
        <p>Under data protection laws (such as <strong>GDPR</strong>, <strong>CCPA</strong>), you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>📌 Access & Review:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data.</li>
            <li><strong>📌 Edit & Update:</strong> Correct any inaccurate information.</li>
            <li><strong>📌 Delete Data:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data (except for legal obligations).</li>
            <li><strong>📌 Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing emails anytime.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To make a request, email us at <strong>fithub888@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

        <h2><strong>7. 📘 Compliance with Privacy Laws</strong></h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>🇪🇺 GDPR</strong> – Applies to European users.</li>
            <li><strong>🇺🇸 CCPA</strong> – Applies to California residents.</li>
            <li><strong>🇲🇾 PDPA</strong> – Applies to Malaysian users.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any concerns about your data, feel free to <strong>contact us.</strong></p>

        <h2><strong>8. 🔁 Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong></h2>
